      the Crystord products without our prior written consent.</p>
      <p>Google Sheets™ and Google Slides™ are trademarks of Google LLC. Aleutheris is not
      affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by Google LLC.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Pricing and Subscriptions</h2>
      <p>The Add-on is currently available free of charge. If paid features are introduced, updated
      terms and a separate notification will be provided before any payment is required. Details of
      any App subscription plans are described within the App at the time of purchase.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Service Availability</h2>
      <p>We aim to maintain reasonable availability of both products but do not guarantee
      uninterrupted service. We reserve the right to carry out maintenance, release updates, or
      modify features with reasonable notice. Service availability may depend on third-party
