      any, for access to the relevant service in the 12 months preceding the claim.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Termination</h2>
      <p>You may terminate use of either product at any time by uninstalling the Add-on, ceasing
      to use the App, or requesting account deletion. We may suspend or terminate your access if
      you breach these Terms or engage in conduct harmful to our services or other users, with or
      without prior notice at our discretion. Termination of the App does not affect your Google
