    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Changes to These Terms</h2>
      <p>We may update these Terms to reflect product changes or legal requirements. Material
      changes will be communicated via this page with an updated revision date. Continued use of
      Crystord products after changes are published constitutes acceptance of the revised Terms.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Governing Law</h2>
      <p>These Terms are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the Netherlands,
      without regard to conflict-of-law provisions. Any disputes shall be subject to the exclusive
      jurisdiction of the competent courts of the Netherlands, unless a mandatory
      consumer-protection law in your country of residence requires otherwise.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Severability</h2>
      <p>If any provision of these Terms is found to be invalid or unenforceable, the remaining
      provisions remain effective to the fullest extent permitted by law.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about these Terms may be directed to Aleutheris at
      <a href={`mailto:${siteConfig.contactEmail}`}>{siteConfig.contactEmail}</a>.</p>
    </section>

    <small slot="trademark">Google Sheets™ and Google Slides™ are trademarks of Google LLC.</small>
  </PolicyArticle>
</MainLayout>
